1
00:00:09,690 --> 00:00:14,690
Robot: "calibration complete"

2
00:00:13,430 --> 00:00:18,430
Robot: "Please be aware that there may be lag times in receiving and processing your requests.  I'll say DONE when I've completed your request, or SENT after sending you a photo, or I may ask for more information or let you know if there is a problem.  You can ask me for help at any time."

3
00:00:21,350 --> 00:00:26,350
CMD: "take a photo"

4
00:00:32,100 --> 00:00:37,100
Robot: "sent"

5
00:00:52,620 --> 00:00:57,620
CMD: "I'm ready"

6
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:16,160
CMD: "move forward a little bit"

7
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:20,080
Robot: "I'm also ready.  What should I do next?  You can tell me to move to an object that you see or to move a certain distance."

8
00:01:21,510 --> 00:01:26,510
Robot: "How far is a little bit?"

9
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:26,520
CMD: "two feet"

10
00:01:37,570 --> 00:01:42,570
Robot: "executing..."

11
00:01:44,490 --> 00:01:49,490
Robot: "done"

12
00:01:53,150 --> 00:01:58,150
CMD: "and then turn left"

13
00:01:59,330 --> 00:02:04,330
CMD: "then take a photo"

14
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:13,400
Robot: "Does a little bit mean two feet?"

15
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:41,600
CMD: "yes it does"

16
00:02:52,660 --> 00:02:57,660
Robot: "How far should I turn left?  Until facing the door to my left?"

17
00:02:57,870 --> 00:03:02,870
CMD: "perpendicular to the doorway"

18
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:32,040
Robot: "executing..."

19
00:03:51,270 --> 00:03:56,270
Robot: "done"

20
00:03:55,180 --> 00:04:00,180
CMD: "take a photo"

21
00:04:04,010 --> 00:04:09,010
Robot: "sent"

22
00:04:04,050 --> 00:04:09,050
CMD: "move around the cone into the next room"

23
00:04:09,010 --> 00:04:14,010
CMD: "turn right ninety degrees"

24
00:04:12,380 --> 00:04:17,380
CMD: "and take a photo"

25
00:04:42,410 --> 00:04:47,410
Robot: "There is not enough space for me to move around the cone and enter the room ahead.  Would you like me to get as close as possible to the room?"

26
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:56,600
CMD: "on the right side of the cone"

27
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:24,420
Robot: "executing..."

28
00:05:24,590 --> 00:05:29,590
Robot: "done"

29
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:29,720
CMD: "turn left about forty five degrees"

30
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:34,400
CMD: "and take a photo"

31
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:44,440
Robot: "executing..."

32
00:05:48,250 --> 00:05:53,250
CMD: "can you tell if there's a doorway in that room"

33
00:05:50,910 --> 00:05:55,910
Robot: "sent"

34
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:26,500
Robot: "My LIDAR map isn't showing any other doorway in the room ahead."

35
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:32,100
CMD: "then turn around one hundred and eighty degrees"

36
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:36,750
CMD: "move forward about two feet"

37
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:39,280
CMD: "then turn left and continue down the hallway you're in"

38
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:07,270
Robot: "How far should I continue down the hallway?"

39
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:43,950
CMD: "continue up to the next opening on your left side"

40
00:07:56,260 --> 00:08:01,260
Robot: "executing..."

41
00:08:12,970 --> 00:08:17,970
CMD: "and take a photo"

42
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:19,720
Robot: "done"

43
00:08:29,900 --> 00:08:34,900
Robot: "executing..."

44
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:41,560
Robot: "sent"

45
00:08:41,920 --> 00:08:46,920
CMD: "and then can you tell what is inside that doorway"

46
00:09:18,410 --> 00:09:23,410
Robot: "You are probably more familiar with the objects inside the doorway than I am.  Should I send a picture after turning to face the doorway?"

47
00:09:25,350 --> 00:09:30,350
CMD: "yes"

48
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:37,790
CMD: "can you get around that object"

49
00:09:35,780 --> 00:09:40,780
Robot: "sent"

50
00:09:50,090 --> 00:09:55,090
Robot: "No, the object is obstructing the doorway."

51
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:59,920
CMD: "turn to your left ninety degrees"

52
00:09:57,070 --> 00:10:02,070
CMD: "and take a photo"

53
00:10:07,710 --> 00:10:12,710
Robot: "executing..."

54
00:10:21,700 --> 00:10:26,700
Robot: "sent"

55
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:51,790
CMD: "go back to the other doorway"

56
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:07,920
Robot: "executing..."

57
00:11:08,770 --> 00:11:13,770
CMD: "face the doorway"

58
00:11:13,310 --> 00:11:18,310
CMD: "and back up until you hit the wall"

59
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:20,800
Robot: "done"

60
00:11:18,570 --> 00:11:23,570
CMD: "or just about hit the wall"

61
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:37,480
Robot: "executing..."

62
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:42,840
CMD: "stop"

63
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:45,560
CMD: "take a photo"

64
00:11:50,010 --> 00:11:55,010
Robot: "done"

65
00:11:54,960 --> 00:11:59,960
Robot: "sent"

66
00:12:03,070 --> 00:12:08,070
CMD: "do the same thing to the other doorway"

67
00:12:12,210 --> 00:12:17,210
Robot: "executing..."

68
00:12:56,650 --> 00:13:01,650
CMD: "move up to that  space between the uh object that blocks the doorway in the doorway itself"

69
00:12:56,950 --> 00:13:01,950
Robot: "sent"

70
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:10,600
CMD: "and take a photo"

71
00:13:14,230 --> 00:13:19,230
Robot: "executing..."

72
00:14:07,260 --> 00:14:12,260
Robot: "sent"

73
00:14:11,550 --> 00:14:16,550
CMD: "and take another photo so i have a clear picture of everything"

74
00:14:32,400 --> 00:14:37,400
Robot: "executing..."

75
00:14:50,320 --> 00:14:55,320
Robot: "sent"

76
00:14:56,600 --> 00:15:01,600
CMD: "go back to where you started"

77
00:15:01,700 --> 00:15:06,700
CMD: "turn a hundred and eighty degrees"

78
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:09,720
CMD: "and take a photo at the entryway"

79
00:15:21,870 --> 00:15:26,870
Robot: "executing..."

80
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:54,900
CMD: "back up a little bit"

81
00:16:03,680 --> 00:16:08,680
Robot: "How far is a little bit?"

82
00:16:05,000 --> 00:16:10,000
CMD: "same thing as before by two feet"

83
00:16:09,170 --> 00:16:14,170
Robot: "Two feet?"

84
00:16:10,380 --> 00:16:15,380
CMD: "you know what make it four"

85
00:16:23,570 --> 00:16:28,570
Robot: "executing..."

86
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:46,600
Robot: "done"

87
00:16:43,810 --> 00:16:48,810
CMD: "take a photo"

88
00:16:55,480 --> 00:17:00,480
Robot: "sent"

89
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:16,400
CMD: "are you sure there's no way to get into the first doorway"

90
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:47,880
Robot: "I'm not sure.  I will return to face the first doorway and send a photo, ok?"

91
00:17:45,070 --> 00:17:50,070
CMD: "no just back up a little bit"

92
00:17:47,740 --> 00:17:52,740
CMD: "and take another photo"

93
00:17:58,540 --> 00:18:03,540
Robot: "Four feet?"

94
00:17:58,630 --> 00:18:03,630
CMD: "two feet this time"

95
00:18:10,980 --> 00:18:15,980
Robot: "executing..."

96
00:18:22,060 --> 00:18:27,060
Robot: "sent"

97
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:46,400
CMD: "go back to the start"

98
00:18:44,940 --> 00:18:49,940
CMD: "and turn around"

99
00:18:46,690 --> 00:18:51,690
CMD: "and do a victory lap"

100
00:19:27,330 --> 00:19:32,330
CMD: "i saw two cones how about you robot"

101
00:19:50,010 --> 00:19:55,010
Robot: "I think you are better at recognizing cones than I am."

